{"tid":2249423,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台方指大陸駐斐濟使館人員闖雙十活動　北京斥賊喊捉賊","createTime":"2020-10-19T10:23:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T11:25:05.000Z","uid":241764,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bd529ceb6990ea5701453710ec34f1d71a3ba2e8","tid":2249423,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T10:23:59.000Z","msg":"兩岸駐斐濟官員日前懷疑發生肢體衝突，雙方互相指責。<br />\n<br />\n台灣表示，駐斐濟代表處日前舉行雙十慶典酒會期間，兩名大陸駐斐濟大使館人員闖入，期間叫囂和拍照，不肯離去，雙方人員肢體衝突，有台方人員受傷，台灣強烈譴責大陸人員的行為，又說大陸人員被斐濟警方帶離現場，但由於有外交豁免權，斐濟警方無進一步行動。<br />\n<br />\n全文:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555560-20201019.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555560-20201019.htm&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9ZjKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=094836b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555560-20201019.htm&h=4328101c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555560-20201019.htm</a>"},{"pid":"7d5cf5785d5b2d1f35d12f5b725e46e79de88796","tid":2249423,"uid":44171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T10:26:46.000Z","msg":"支那人無啦啦會去台灣酒會，唔通係台灣叫佢去咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1378b047bd36dca3fe4329cefa0a0c43815c617d","tid":2249423,"uid":356914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T10:48:01.000Z","msg":"屌 指鹿為馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4491bbee85d98bf10f37be246d725f18b2e849b4","tid":2249423,"uid":121197,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T10:59:16.000Z","msg":"台仔心諗下次真係閂埋門往死裡打柒番個支那外交官好過"},{"pid":"30b25dfd1ca94d4e78148d8d1d0dd23ba9e7ea52","tid":2249423,"uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:00:56.000Z","msg":"實係冇CCTV等你亂吹水"},{"pid":"4100095b64ab1ce3e95023162e230d31d52af3d7","tid":2249423,"uid":367280,"like":0,